titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: CYTOLOGY AND OR CORE BIOPSY RESULT NOT KNOWN (PERCENTAGE OF REFERRED) - Description

div.p: CYTOLOGY AND OR CORE BIOPSY RESULT NOT KNOWN (PERCENTAGE OF REFERRED) is the percentage of women referred for one or more cytology and/or core Biopsy procedures, for whom a definite result is not recorded and an open Biopsy is not indicated.
